&lt;li&gt;Perform system updates and coordinate with development teams on module enhancements and customizations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to and resolve customer support tickets related to cloud resources, billing, and portal access, minimizing escalations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provision and troubleshoot cloud resources, including virtual machines, storage, and clusters; assist customers with configuration, connectivity, and performance issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document recurring issues and create structured support content for knowledge base publication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gather customer feedback and usage trends to identify improvements in portal functionality, billing workflows, and cloud services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with backend engineering on escalations, providing detailed diagnostics and reproduction steps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
