&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience administering Odoo ERP, including billing, subscriptions, CRM, and customer portal modules.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to configure workflows, customize views, and manage user access within Odoo.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of cloud computing concepts, including virtual machines, storage, and clustering, across platforms such as AWS, GCP, Azure, or similar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong troubleshooting skills with the ability to resolve technical issues independently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and customer support skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience documenting technical issues and creating knowledge base content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with ticketing systems and CRM tools for issue tracking and escalation management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to collaborate effectively with cross-functional technical teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to stay current with Odoo updates and cloud technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Odoo certification or equivalent hands-on expertise in customization and administration.&lt;/li&gt;
