&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience in back-end development, including strong experience building production systems at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of experience with object-oriented programming languages, including 5+ years working with PHP and modern PHP practices such as PHP 8+.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience with MySQL, including schema design, indexing, and query optimization, along with hands-on experience using caching systems such as Memcached and Redis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-depth understanding of web development fundamentals, HTTP protocols, and Linux server environments, including reading logs and troubleshooting production issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of front-end technologies such as JavaScript or TypeScript, HTML, and CSS, along with the willingness to jump into any project when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Preferred Qualifications&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with video technologies, containers, codecs, or live streaming environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with NGINX, WebSocket-based communication, BASH scripting, networking fundamentals, or static analysis tools such as PHPStan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience modernizing legacy PHP applications, working with server-side rendering architectures, or contributing to CI/CD and automated testing practices such as PHPUnit.&lt;/li&gt;
