&lt;li&gt;Experience designing and implementing backend services and APIs, including REST and GraphQL, for complex applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong systems design skills and the ability to operate with a high degree of autonomy in complex, multi-service architectures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with containerization and orchestration technologies such as Docker and Kubernetes, and comfort owning deployment practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong debugging and problem-solving skills across application, data, and infrastructure layers, including production incident diagnosis and mitigation.&lt;/li&gt;
